@user4 @user3 You can do it! And I'm happy to help you with my experiences.
Website: Check out @user5. It seems simple, looks good, and is open source. I will switch one of my websites to it before the next renewal.
Signal: Check out cal.com. It's an open-source calendar service with integrations that allow planning of video calls with Element Call, JITSI, and so on. Signal is also supported, but I haven't tested whether it's for messages or videos yet.
I can recommend @user6. End-to-end encryption, decentralized, open source.
